Comment: 0,0:16:43.09,0:16:45.43,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You think that's bad? Think about what would have happened if she sang "TORCH".
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.54,0:00:24.97,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Don't you need to let the old man and Sanae-san know that we're leaving?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.98,0:00:35.64,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Those pictures…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.64,0:00:36.33,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.75,0:00:40.57,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,My dad used to be an actor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.57,0:00:43.56,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,He was famous from his\Nhigh school days in student drama.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.29,0:00:47.05,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Apparently, he won competitions, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.16,0:00:50.58,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I never knew any of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.58,0:00:54.51,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Though, I was told that Mom\Nused to teach at a middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.00,0:01:04.29,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,The two people in the pictures looked like they were enjoying their lives. {ep 21}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.29,0:01:06.89,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Of course, since they were living out their dreams. {ep 21}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.89,0:01:07.91,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Nagisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.91,0:01:11.71,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,And it was supposed to last forever… {ep 21}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.43,0:01:14.89,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,…if only I weren't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.89,0:01:16.03,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You're wrong! {ep 21}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.03,0:01:18.69,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Besides, they're enjoying their lives right now, too! {ep 21}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.69,0:01:21.08,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,But they gave up on their dreams. {ep 21}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.08,0:01:22.23,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Am I wrong? {ep 21}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.16,0:01:30.95,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,And right now, I'm trying to live\Nmy own dream when I sacrificed theirs. {ep 21}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.77,0:01:33.93,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm a terrible child.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.93,0:01:35.20,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,What an ungrateful child.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.64,0:01:37.58,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,It's the same with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.03,0:01:43.56,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I've asked so much of everyone's time to grant my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.09,0:01:46.27,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,We're doing it because we want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.57,0:01:50.98,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,If you quit now, all that we've done will go to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.47,0:01:54.95,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,We've worked hard together this far,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.95,0:01:55.97,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,so let's finish strong.
