Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.62,0:03:32.25,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(965.455,724.5)}Two Shadows
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.69,0:03:52.58,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,I'm really sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.58,0:03:54.42,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,You're not feeling nervous at all, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.42,0:03:56.74,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Nagisa-chan, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.42,0:04:00.39,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Nagisa's getting nervous about the performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.39,0:04:01.20,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.20,0:04:02.68,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.34,0:04:05.83,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Isn't something strange about Nagisa-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.83,0:04:07.68,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Some stuff happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.68,0:04:09.56,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Just act like you always do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.94,0:04:17.10,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Nagisa-chan, I'll teach you a good charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.10,0:04:19.71,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Write a character on your hand three times and swallow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.71,0:04:21.95,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Person. Person. Person.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.95,0:04:24.38,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,You're writing “enter” instead of “person”.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.99,0:04:24.38,Note,Note,0,0,0,,Note: Person = {\fs64.8}人{\r} Enter = {\fs64.8}入{\r}\NKanji with different stroke order and orientation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.38,0:04:25.99,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,It's the thought that counts! The thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.99,0:04:29.25,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Youhei, if you can't write kanji, then you don't have to try.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.25,0:04:30.61,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Of course I can write at this level!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.61,0:04:31.71,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.71,0:04:33.15,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,You're making fun of me too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.15,0:04:36.57,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,The performance is in the afternoon, so why don't you go out for a walk?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.57,0:04:38.83,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,That's right, I have to go meet my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.83,0:04:41.46,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Then it'll be free time until we have to meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.38,0:04:44.62,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,So, where do you want to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.73,0:04:47.71,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Nagisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.17,0:04:50.56,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.14,0:04:56.76,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I know I have to get my act straight,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.20,0:04:59.27,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,but I can't help but think about other things…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.85,0:05:03.90,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,You're right, Okazaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.28,0:05:10.79,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,It's a performance that we've made together, so I can't go ruining it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.04,0:05:14.39,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yeah, let's give it our best.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.39,0:05:15.29,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.56,0:05:38.97,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Okazaki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.61,0:05:41.95,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Where did she go?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.72,0:05:44.87,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Sanae-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.58,0:05:47.24,San,San,0,0,0,,Oh, Okazaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.24,0:05:49.46,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,The old man's not with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.46,0:05:52.33,San,San,0,0,0,,No, he told me to go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.76,0:05:54.59,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Will he come…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.59,0:05:59.23,San,San,0,0,0,,There's nothing to worry about!\NWe wouldn't miss Nagisa's performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.16,0:06:03.31,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,She found out everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.83,0:06:06.39,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It was too late by the time I found her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.18,0:06:09.51,San,San,0,0,0,,Where is Nagisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.51,0:06:11.37,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Actually, we got separated.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.37,0:06:12.28,San,San,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.28,0:06:13.66,Default,Iso,0,0,0,,Furukawa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.31,0:06:16.38,San,San,0,0,0,,Isogai-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.05,0:06:19.12,San,San,0,0,0,,Well then, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.12,0:06:22.00,San,San,0,0,0,,Please take care of Nagisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.26,0:06:39.67,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.75,0:06:42.31,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,Oh, Furukawa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.31,0:06:43.88,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,What brings you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.42,0:06:46.61,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Um, well…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.73,0:06:56.25,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I heard from Okazaki-san before that this place has recordings of high school theatrical plays.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.92,0:07:01.66,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,Are you going to use it as a reference for your play?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.66,0:07:02.50,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.50,0:07:05.35,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to seeing your performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.35,0:07:06.78,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.30,0:07:07.98,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.16,0:07:12.82,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,I'll be out for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.82,0:07:15.80,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,Feel free to look at any references or videos.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.33,0:07:18.30,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.82,0:07:25.77,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Miyazawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.51,0:07:28.06,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,Oh, Okazaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.06,0:07:29.70,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Have you seen Nagisa anywhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.70,0:07:34.73,Yuk,Yuk,0,0,0,,Furukawa-san is in the Resource Room,\Nlooking at recordings of old high school drama.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.42,0:07:38.60,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Nagisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.18,0:07:41.17,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,{\an8}If my life had ended then, I wouldn't have had to answer the Sphinx's riddle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.50,0:07:49.17,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,{\an8}Nor would I have had to hurl my father and mother to the abyss of calamity…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.17,0:07:50.59,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,{\an8}…and make them face a fatal destiny!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.36,0:07:56.45,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,{\an8}People of Thebes! Look well!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.81,0:07:56.45,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Is this the old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.45,0:08:00.25,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,It's a video of when Dad was in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.84,0:08:04.75,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,It's when we won the drama competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.45,0:08:04.10,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,{\an8}Witness how much of an ungrateful being I am towards those who have been grateful to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.75,0:08:13.79,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,{\an8}Apollo has forsaken me, now a symbol of stigma that brings misfortune to myself and all citizens!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.73,0:08:16.14,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,{\an8}Witness!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.14,0:08:24.71,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,{\an8}Your very own king was the source of all the calamity that leads this world to evil. To Hades!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.14,0:08:17.97,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,He's really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.55,0:08:24.26,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,He's a senior just like me, but he's incomparably better.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.26,0:08:33.85,Default,Woman,0,0,0,,Let's now hear a word from\Nthe club president, Furukawa-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.76,0:08:35.72,Default,Woman,0,0,0,,A word from you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.33,0:08:41.83,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,I love drama!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.83,0:08:44.73,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,I will continue to stand on the stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.73,0:08:49.46,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,I will take this moment to swear that I will become a professional actor!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.46,0:08:54.51,Default,Woman,0,0,0,,Um, could you leave your personal ambition at that and give a word as the president of the club?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.51,0:08:56.58,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Drama is the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.68,0:09:01.34,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You are who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.73,0:09:04.26,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You have to do what you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.73,0:09:05.69,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.43,0:09:22.37,Default-alt,PA,0,0,0,,That concludes the Choir Club's performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.84,0:09:25.12,Default-alt,PA,0,0,0,,Next is a solo play by the drama club.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.12,0:09:26.63,Default-alt,PA,0,0,0,,“Fantasia Story”
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.39,0:09:30.47,Default-alt,PA,0,0,0,,Written and performed by Furukawa Nagisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.91,0:09:33.24,Default-alt,PA,0,0,0,,Please stand by until the stage is set.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.81,0:09:47.84,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Nagisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.84,0:09:50.02,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,The time's come.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.02,0:09:52.94,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Don't worry. You'll definitely do well out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.94,0:09:56.21,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Everything will go well as long as you do as you practiced.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.21,0:09:58.98,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Don't stress over it too much and enjoy yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.98,0:09:59.87,Default,Bot,0,0,0,,Puhi puhi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.46,0:10:13.99,Default-alt,PA,0,0,0,,Thank you for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.99,0:10:16.43,Default-alt,PA,0,0,0,,“Fantasia Story” by the drama club.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.54,0:10:18.40,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Nagisa…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.24,0:10:20.18,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.78,0:10:42.08,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I want to find out what it is. {ep 19}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.08,0:10:43.66,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I want to know about it and apologize. {ep 19}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.37,0:10:47.05,San,San,0,0,0,,Leave it to me. {ep 21}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.37,0:10:48.58,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Nagisa-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.58,0:10:50.33,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,I rented a good thing for you. {ep 21}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.33,0:10:50.85,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Here. {ep 21}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.09,0:10:53.25,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Something's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.25,0:10:56.39,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Welcome back, the fruit of our love. {ep 21}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.87,0:10:59.05,Default,People,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.05,0:11:00.14,Default,People,0,0,0,,Maybe she's nervous?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.14,0:11:02.39,Tom,Tom,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Get your act together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.39,0:11:05.06,Kot,Kot,0,0,0,,Something's wrong with Nagisa-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.06,0:11:07.46,Ryo,Ryo,0,0,0,,Maybe she's become too nervous?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.46,0:11:08.77,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,Okazaki, what should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.77,0:11:10.44,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Should we drop the curtain?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.11,0:11:13.40,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,No, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.51,0:11:16.44,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,She will do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.44,0:11:20.25,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,I love drama!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.24,0:11:22.00,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,I love drama!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.55,0:11:23.31,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,I will continue to stand on the stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.81,0:11:25.55,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,I will continue to stand on the stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.55,0:11:28.40,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,I will take this moment to swear that I will beco—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.37,0:11:30.90,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,I will take this moment to swear that I will beco—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.90,0:11:32.82,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,I will take this moment to swear that I will beco—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.07,0:11:35.18,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Drama is the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.78,0:11:37.58,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Drama is the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.85,0:11:38.70,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Drama is the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.58,0:11:41.91,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Drama is the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.53,0:12:00.25,Default,People,0,0,0,,Did the play start?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.25,0:12:01.82,Default,People,0,0,0,,No way. Is she crying for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.57,0:12:05.16,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,This isn't good! Let's drop the curtain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.16,0:12:06.05,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Tomoya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.37,0:12:23.51,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Make your dream come true, Nagisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.67,0:12:26.53,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.53,0:12:27.06,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.06,0:12:28.52,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Nagisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.50,0:12:31.56,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Are you an idiot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.02,0:12:34.31,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,A child's dream is their parents' dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.31,0:12:36.07,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,So grant it for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.07,0:12:39.68,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,We've been dreaming of the day you would make your dream come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.11,0:12:42.76,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,We didn't give up our dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.76,0:12:45.28,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,We changed our dreams to your dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.72,0:12:47.91,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,That's what parents are!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.91,0:12:50.58,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,That's what family is!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.20,0:12:53.57,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,So… ever since that day…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.06,0:12:55.85,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Every day, while baking bread…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.63,0:13:00.38,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,…we've been living, waiting for this day!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.38,0:13:03.93,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,If you fail here, we'll be depressed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.93,0:13:05.18,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Do you hear me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.18,0:13:08.78,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,You've got a huge responsibility on your back, you hear me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.78,0:13:10.52,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Sanae! You're here, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.52,0:13:11.89,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,You say something, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.47,0:13:14.76,San,San,0,0,0,,Nagisa! You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.98,0:13:17.87,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,What? What is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.87,0:13:18.65,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Tomoya!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.14,0:13:22.86,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Same goes for us, Nagisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.86,0:13:27.73,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,You're about to make something happen that Sunohara and I couldn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.73,0:13:31.87,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Right now, you're even carrying the burdens of failure that we held!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.49,0:14:05.81,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Shall I…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.49,0:14:09.16,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Shall I take you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.74,0:14:15.12,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,To the place in this city where wishes come true? {ep1}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.75,0:14:17.65,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Take us there, Nagisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.70,0:14:19.74,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Take us away.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.08,0:14:23.95,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,This is a world that has ended. {ep 21}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.55,0:14:27.18,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,A world where no one exists aside from myself. {ep 21}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.99,0:14:31.67,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,This room only contains a small wooden table and chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.25,0:14:35.98,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Beyond the window is a barren and expansive plain. {ep 21}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.15,0:14:42.19,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,This building is old, with no evidence to suggest when it was actually built.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.22,0:14:45.86,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I live alone in this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.59,0:14:50.20,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I sometimes go out to gather necessities.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.24,0:14:56.46,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,There is no one to be found outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.41,0:15:01.61,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Within the faint sunlight float many small lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.25,0:15:08.15,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I gathered pieces of wood, nails,\Nand a variety of other things.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.47,0:15:10.29,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,It's all for the sake of creating a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.20,0:15:17.10,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,But, will the one being born be happy about entering this kind of world?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.54,0:15:20.83,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Holding that doubt within…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.12,0:15:28.07,Default,Robo,0,0,0,,This world had indeed ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.34,0:15:31.29,Default,Robo,0,0,0,,No more lives will be born.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.29,0:15:33.97,Default,Robo,0,0,0,,She's the only being with life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.58,0:15:40.43,Default,Robo,0,0,0,,Either in the distant past or the distant future,\NI was in a different place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.95,0:15:43.63,Default,Robo,0,0,0,,It was a very lively place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.22,0:15:46.38,Default,Robo,0,0,0,,But I can no longer return there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.92,0:15:50.29,Default,Robo,0,0,0,,I have this body she made for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.31,0:15:53.55,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.89,0:15:57.10,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Are you going to make another one?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.85,0:16:03.12,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,But it won't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.60,0:16:06.23,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,You can't make any friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.49,0:16:11.86,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,You're going to make something else?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.62,0:16:15.87,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,What will you make?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.40,0:16:18.67,Default,Robo,0,0,0,,I don't know that, myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.02,0:16:24.55,Default,Robo,0,0,0,,But she has the ability to collect junk and make something new.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.13,0:16:28.08,Default,Robo,0,0,0,,It's something special that I can't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.36,0:16:31.96,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.96,0:16:36.64,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,With time, we might be able to make something nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.39,0:16:41.39,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,What should we make?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.58,0:16:51.49,Default,Robo,0,0,0,,Something that's exciting like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.07,0:16:54.49,Default,Robo,0,0,0,,She will make it, and I will help.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.80,0:16:56.87,Default,Robo,0,0,0,,It will be an incredibly wonderful thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.83,0:17:00.24,Default,Robo,0,0,0,,I will stay by her side.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.24,0:17:02.61,Default,Robo,0,0,0,,I'll continue to be with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.33,0:17:06.63,Default,Robo,0,0,0,,And one day, we'll leave this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.63,0:17:11.54,Default,Robo,0,0,0,,We'll go to the warm, lively world where I used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.19,0:17:28.90,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I remembered the rest of the story!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.91,0:17:31.90,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,The rest of the story goes…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.90,0:17:36.91,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,The girl and the doll decide to leave that world,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.91,0:17:43.66,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,because the doll knows of a warmer,\Nlivelier world far away from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.66,0:17:45.39,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,What happens then?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.34,0:17:49.67,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,They go on a long, long journey, and at the end…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.67,0:17:50.91,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,At the end?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.41,0:17:52.74,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,…they sing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.47,0:17:54.61,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.61,0:17:55.93,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.93,0:18:02.38,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,So, I was right to sing at the end of the play.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.38,0:18:06.69,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,But I'm sure that the girl would have sung something other than “Big Dango Family”.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.69,0:18:08.55,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,That's because I wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.55,0:18:13.09,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Everyone was clapping, but there was\Na strange air in the auditorium in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.09,0:18:15.43,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It sort of ruined all the emotional things that built up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.41,0:18:19.02,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I wanted to sing no matter what, so…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.60,0:18:22.89,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Oh well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.93,0:18:25.83,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Your play was great.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.83,0:18:27.62,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Do you mean it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.62,0:18:30.21,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I never flatter. You know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.21,0:18:31.73,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.06,0:18:34.47,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,So, I'm happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.47,0:18:41.53,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,You came.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.06,0:18:44.39,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Yes, since I got the invitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.40,0:18:47.79,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for doing it without telling you,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.10,0:18:51.00,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,but I thought I should let him know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.69,0:18:53.66,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,I watched your play.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.66,0:18:55.15,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,It was a good story.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.15,0:18:56.60,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.54,0:19:00.41,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,It reminded me of a lot of my past.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.55,0:19:06.54,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Well then, I'll be going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.54,0:19:07.50,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.04,0:19:10.78,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Don't drink too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.63,0:19:19.22,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Okazaki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.60,0:19:24.92,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Tomorrow, let's go somewhere, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.47,0:19:27.39,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It'll be the make-up vacation day, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.39,0:19:29.30,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Once in a while, we should go out somewhere, just the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.62,0:19:30.98,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I have something I need to talk with you about, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.98,0:19:32.31,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.73,0:19:33.69,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,So this is where you two were!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.69,0:19:35.80,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,Everyone's waiting in the club room!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.80,0:19:38.65,Kyo,Kyo,0,0,0,,If we don't have the actor and Effects there,\Nwe can't start the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.65,0:19:40.09,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Sorry about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.85,0:19:41.66,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.11,0:19:42.88,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.20,0:20:07.89,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Is it all right for us to come in without permission?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.89,0:20:11.48,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,It's fine. We're students at this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.84,0:20:12.92,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.09,0:20:16.90,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Recently…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.50,0:20:21.98,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Recently, I haven't hated this school anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.98,0:20:25.09,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Really? That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.04,0:20:29.34,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I'm on duty?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.20,0:20:32.35,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I wrote that when you were absent.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.35,0:20:33.25,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I forgot about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.60,0:20:36.17,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I never noticed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.59,0:20:52.05,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Payback.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.29,0:20:53.29,Note,Nag,0,0,0,,{\pos(580.909,177.75)}On Duty - Furukawa Nagisa - Okazaki Tomoya
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.17,0:21:00.62,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Yesterday, I told you that I had to talk with you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.97,0:21:02.78,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,Yes, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.30,0:21:06.16,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Um… How should I put it…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.39,0:21:10.87,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Would…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.87,0:21:16.66,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Wouldn't it be interesting to say that\Nwe're dating when we wake up tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.70,0:21:25.97,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,Please date me, Nagisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.50,0:21:28.62,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.62,0:21:32.59,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,So, I want you to always be with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.87,0:23:43.84,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)\pos(981.818,452.25)\c&HFFFFFF&\be2\4c&H000000&\3c&H454845&\bord3.15}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.72,0:24:09.70,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(981.818,384.75)\c&HFFFFFF&\be2\4c&H000000&\3c&H454845&\bord3.15}Extra Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.72,0:24:09.70,Titles,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(981.818,767.25)\c&HFFFFFF&\be2\4c&H000000&\3c&H454845&\bord3.15}What Happened Over the Summer Break
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.70,0:23:46.62,Nag,Nag,0,0,0,,I heard that Okazaki-san will be going over to Sunohara-san's today.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.62,0:23:48.33,Sun,Sun,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Okazaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.88,0:23:53.08,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,I've been starting to think about you a lot these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.08,0:23:55.07,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,Looks like fun…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.07,0:23:57.21,Aki,Aki,0,0,0,,I wonder if I could join in.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.21,0:23:59.59,Oka,Oka,0,0,0,,There isn't anyone around, so don't worry.
